In this text i will talk about the NFT. The NFT is "non-fungible token", it's not a reel object but he have a value, it's the opposite of a reel money. The NFT can be lot of thing like a image, picture, text, song or vidéo, in short all that can be on internet. Each NFT have a series number that allows to identificate him. When you buy an NFT, you have all the right on him, you can use it to do what you want. A lot of people buy an NFT for reseal after when he take value, whith that, people can have a lot of money.  On today the NFT can have a astronomicale price like 10 000 $ or more and the celebrity start to create there own NFT. The NFT of the celebrity have automaticly a big value because of course that's a celebrity. Some NFT was sale at a millions of dollars. The NFT is already in the video games, in effet, in some vidéo games you can buy and sale a creature who have a value, and because each NFT is unique, you are the only who have this creature. Over the years the NFT can take a big place in internet and,  new concepts can appears in link whith the NFT. In exemple, some french rappers have a virtual appartement in which he exposed his own NfT on the wall of the appartement. To summarize the NFT can be like a investissement in the property but at the place of an appartement you have a non-fungible token.
 For me the NFT is very hard to understand because it's complicated to imagine that a simple image of a monkey can have a very big price. And it's more harder to imagine that a person can win here life whit this NFT. But this can be a good thing in the future because the internet in a parrallel world for me, and i think it's normal to win his life in this world whith new technic. But i also understand the people who think that's ridiculous. The NFT are therefore a good thing to the creator who want to sell his work.
